  <title>xcb-proto-&xcb-proto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The xcb-proto package provides the XML-XCB protocol descriptions that
      libxcb uses to generate the majority of its code and API.
    </para>

